tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ethical_ai_decisions (
	aid DECIMAL PRIMARY KEY,
	description VARCHAR(255),
	date DECIMAL,
	approach VARCHAR(50),
	impact VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE ethical_considerations_ai_decision_making (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   decision_process_name VARCHAR(255),
   ethical_framework VARCHAR(255),
   decision_made_by VARCHAR(255),
   ethical_issues TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE ethical_rating (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    rating INT,
    details TEXT,
    decision_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (decision_id) REFERENCES ethical_considerations_ai_decision_making(id)
);
